Dominique Valadié https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dominique_Valadi%C3%A9 0 Dominique Valadié (born 1952) is a French actress. She studied acting at the Conservatoire national supérieur d'art dramatique in Paris. Valadié has been a lecturer at the Conservatoire national supérieur d'art dramatique since 1983.
